title: KMSAuto Lite 1.3.9 !{Latest}
description:
KMSAuto Lite 1.3.9 !{Latest}

KMSAuto Lite is a KMS-activator for Windows VL operating systems: Vista, 7, 8, 8.1, 10, Server 2008, 2008 R2, 2012, 2012 R2 and Office 2010, 2013. It is possible to activate Office 2010 VL on Windows XP.

Switches open access to the installation of GVLK keys and the configuration of the task scheduler

** Keys are forced, parameters can be applied all together.
*** You can only convert RETAIL -> VL to non-activated office products.

On the Settings tab, you can specify an external KMS-Service address. The service built into the program will not be started when activated.

If activation fails 0xc004f074, make sure that your firewall does not prohibit connections to your KMS-Service. If you create a task in the scheduler for re-activation (in the program for this special tab), the program itself can be moved wherever you want, you can even completely remove it, it is not needed to be re-activated.

Changes in the version:
- Changes in the interface.
